<Algorithm code="           1. If _O_.[[ContentType]] is ~bigint~, let _numValue_ be ? ToBigInt(_value_).           1. Otherwise, let _numValue_ be ? ToNumber(_value_).           1. If IsValidIntegerIndex(_O_, _index_) is *true*, then             1. Let _offset_ be _O_.[[ByteOffset]].             1. Let _elementSize_ be TypedArrayElementSize(_O_).             1. Let _byteIndexInBuffer_ be (ℝ(_index_) × _elementSize_) + _offset_.             1. Let _elementType_ be TypedArrayElementType(_O_).             1. Perform SetValueInBuffer(_O_.[[ViewedArrayBuffer]], _byteIndexInBuffer_, _elementType_, _numValue_, *true*, ~unordered~).           1. Return ~unused~.         ">
   <head>
